  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1342090/extras/4726f398ec79fec273689baeadc52b38.avif?t=1749380861\" width=620 height=76 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1342090/extras/dc7841a521a9c937fc55f267ec39d0b8.poster.avif?t=1749380861\" width=620 height=472 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1342090/extras/dc7841a521a9c937fc55f267ec39d0b8.webm?t=1749380861\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1342090/extras/bb28d727429c1bd57492b3990603479c.avif?t=1749380861\" width=620 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1342090/extras/92d672edd99afcf2d20a0a8dc55fe790.avif?t=1749380861\" width=616 height=72 /></span>A lone wanderer returns to his hometown after years of traveling. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A monster attack leads him to a hidden cave where he's told that</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >the world is in danger... And he's the only one who can save it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel the land and fight off enemies in a race against time. Can you and your</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >companions protect the Crystals from the Empire's nefarious plans? And</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >what about the mysterious voice you keep hearing?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How is it all connected? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1342090/extras/1a06f4f9cb7acdac06aad19a3d88136f.avif?t=1749380861\" width=616 height=72 /></span>Level up, learn new abilities, and use the Job system to customize your party</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >to gain an advantage against your enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock different endings depending on which of the girls you decide to</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >romance and the choices you make on your adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1342090/extras/729d683c6d5c77d3f71a74c4903080f0.avif?t=1749380861\" width=616 height=72 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1342090/extras/17cb3e98a2c8a552392bd6a29aa93aa3.avif?t=1749380861\" width=616 height=399 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1342090/extras/7d06bb7a12a310356fbd5b600fa048e0.avif?t=1749380861\" width=616 height=399 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1342090/extras/9e7de6ae4c995d9466df75cad8b6c6c8.avif?t=1749380861\" width=616 height=72 /></span><strong>A Fantasy Role-Playing Game</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level up and equip your heroes to overcome powerful enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Varied Job System</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick which job suits your needs. Learn unique abilities to turn your</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >party into monster-killing machines.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Large World to Explore</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the main quest through many different lands and unlock side quests along the way.</p>",
